{"tid":614746,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【盡量多圖少字】一個人係台灣電單車環島行","createTime":"2018-04-02T19:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T06:28:27.000Z","uid":14810,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"69ccd3b7fb570e4771ff588d50c978c6574192bb","tid":614746,"uid":14810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T19:33:21.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟我呢就係台灣住左（住埋右）差唔多四年了，今年台灣四月頭就有成10日連假慢慢玩，見有咁長假就緊係直接環島啦。由於本人冇其他巴打有強勁既大腿同臂彎，所以就冇踩單車而選擇電單車相對比較自由同舒服既玩法。今次個trip最希望係走一轉台灣好出名既南迴公路，台東既濱海公路同埋多良車站，希望可以影多啲靚相啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大緻上多良個景係咁樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/123009_84f9be7795002e7b698c0ea110d6578d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F123009_84f9be7795002e7b698c0ea110d6578d.jpg&h=3f1929ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 1:<br />\n台北-&gt;台中 約177公里  因為張圖係計埋上高速公路，所以實際上要4個多鐘頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/121421_2e9df3cdc619d4ca1775628e56f3a2b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F121421_2e9df3cdc619d4ca1775628e56f3a2b0.jpg&h=9f1c3d3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身打算早少少出發，結果一個唔小心訓到成1點半，好在出發前一晚已經整理好曬行李，跟手係campus附近食完野就快快手起行，結果食完都差唔多3點了。雖然google既路線推薦走台三線既山線，但我選擇台61線既濱海快速公路，貪佢啲路夠直又冇咩紅燈。<br />\n<br />\n繼續之前先講下台灣既道路同埋電單車分級先，咁電單車有分開三種牌照，一係50CC以下既小型電單車牌，二係50CC以上250CC以下既普通重型電單車牌同埋最後250CC以上既大型重型電單車牌。咁前兩種係唔需要上駕駛學院既堂就可以考既，而且就出曬名簡單易pass，換句話說你尻考都過到，而大型重型電單車牌就好似香港咁一樣要上堂考試。50CC既車後面個牌係綠色，50以上250以下就白色，250以上就550以下就黃色，550以上就紅色，係唔係好撚複雜呢<br />\n<br />\n而一般道路較常見有藍底白字既省級道路，紅底白字既快速道路、同埋白底梅花樣既高速公路。因為偉大（ON9）既台灣政府關係，所有電單車係冇得上高速公路，冇錯就算你揸goldwing或是H2R呢類superbike，高速公路都係冇你份。而上面提到既紅色牌同黃色牌既電單車可以行紅底白字既快速道路。咁由於小弟係窮L一名，坐駕只係得200CC，所以就冇得上快速道路，只可以乖乖地行一般既省級道路了。<br />\n<br />\n好啦番翻黎個trip到先，咁一路向南沿住海線咁行，一路上都係啲生卡拉既地方，人又少車又少，不過勝在氣溫算唔錯天氣又唔差，沿途上算係幾舒服同自在，真係好似姐輪一邊聽一路向北一路揸住架86既感覺，不過我就揸任架老電一路向南啦<br />\n<br />\n大緻上一路上都係差唔多既景色，上面條高架就係快速道路，可惜這些機會不是屬於我的<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/014636_c44a8e960265963191a403333e6264eb.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F014636_c44a8e960265963191a403333e6264eb.JPG&h=4d4ff05d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大約揸左差唔多2個鐘到就到新竹，時間就差唔多係5點30，係個邊搵左間七仔買支水休息一下順便去附近既南寮漁港睇埋日落再起行。<br />\n<br />\n行李就一個backpack加支結他，無計啦road trip緊係要配支結他先有feel架麻<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/015246_9b254cfae71218e8cbe5b63b268e4483.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F015246_9b254cfae71218e8cbe5b63b268e4483.JPG&h=8c403fd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到漁港果邊時間就差唔多，個天都開始變黃<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/020501_368d9b153df1b9f88baf7a1fc8285dd2.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F020501_368d9b153df1b9f88baf7a1fc8285dd2.JPG&h=b6fd1a1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n順手幫自己架車影一兩張相啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/020626_4fe86309402432972d900f9db8981b58.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F020626_4fe86309402432972d900f9db8981b58.JPG&h=03cca995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海濱旁邊既濕地又既好坐既，順手拎支結他黎撚番幾下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/020805_9b44a96f3e03e2327e7cd5ced4aeb407.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F020805_9b44a96f3e03e2327e7cd5ced4aeb407.JPG&h=b4cd3089&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/024315_98ee0c235f16c47812001e784405ca9a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F024315_98ee0c235f16c47812001e784405ca9a.JPG&h=ba49a294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁睇完日落都差唔多成6點幾，計番就差唔多仲有2個幾鐘頭既車程，跟手就出發啦，一路上除左大風就係大風，仲有一大堆蚊，因為天都黑曬所以沿途都冇咩點影到相，希望快手到台中可以休息一下。<br />\n<br />\n終於到台中市區啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/024841_b2f700cacc37405a0a3c6695a1f1da6d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F024841_b2f700cacc37405a0a3c6695a1f1da6d.JPG&h=3368ee05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到民宿跟手沖番個靚涼然後係common room食出面買既拉麵，咁啱坐我對面既荷蘭人聞到之後話好香，跟著順便就吹下水啦，講起原來佢得20歲，讀緊機械工程，今年有長假一放就幾個月。有時真係好撚葡萄外國人放親假都鬼咁長，仲要歐元係香港台灣又好洗好用，叫我呢啲窮J情何以堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講真佢又OK靚仔既，難怪佢話佢係Tinder識唔少女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/031414_46306f8d0c6acc82d5a02bddbd3e3da6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F031414_46306f8d0c6acc82d5a02bddbd3e3da6.jpg&h=1b646f74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日去到呢度先，聽日應該再係台中stay多一日，之後就去台南，希望巴打支持下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5cbe873492753f765f1caa23066ebda53945737","tid":614746,"uid":14810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T02:50:37.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0333a05536dbc72f52279134b9deb2787f385dc8","tid":614746,"uid":158932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T02:56:41.000Z","msg":"我都想黎個一個月台灣環島遊 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f6b0c73e710c2bf01232014094e32f0f747b3b","tid":614746,"uid":88651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:07:35.000Z","msg":"［member]lm[/member]"},{"pid":"a3b6856d0d33993f6049ff5727778a3a1ed7566b","tid":614746,"uid":14810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0333a05536dbc72f52279134b9deb2787f385dc8","tid":614746,"uid":158932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T02:56:41.000Z","msg":"我都想黎個一個月台灣環島遊 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:37:26.000Z","msg":"其實真係好值得去環島，無論用咩方法都好，旅行既過程都係一種既經驗，一般人去台灣只係stay一兩個城市，大部分都係台北台中同高雄，我覺得東部三個城市先最有台灣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6a058bc2d11d7ae75f5ac97085251e70090284","tid":614746,"uid":14810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T07:31:20.000Z","msg":"話說小弟依家落緊墾丁啦，沿路上真係太撚靚忍唔住share左相先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/05/152620_1399749759b38357cc054c58f6102079.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F05%2F152620_1399749759b38357cc054c58f6102079.png&h=2671c9e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/05/153103_f13647f680d7be6abd27812a4df91ac8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F05%2F153103_f13647f680d7be6abd27812a4df91ac8.png&h=a0fdc8fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/05/153107_91bf101557126a750afd183a5b8d395e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F05%2F153107_91bf101557126a750afd183a5b8d395e.png&h=15de4c15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15828df4cb3b9ae5bde291817cc9cede4e4888ae","tid":614746,"uid":179367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T06:07:34.000Z","msg":"巴打還安好？"},{"pid":"9d841a49275d33c952acbb95b73361d2fec6cbe1","tid":614746,"uid":14810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"15828df4cb3b9ae5bde291817cc9cede4e4888ae","tid":614746,"uid":179367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T06:07:34.000Z","msg":"巴打還安好？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T19:50:39.000Z","msg":"Hey巴打我係度，因為最近搞緊畢業展覽所以冇咩點update、同埋個post真係冇咩人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a22cb9c99055f5bf292b3de4e77a65364751660","tid":614746,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d841a49275d33c952acbb95b73361d2fec6cbe1","tid":614746,"uid":14810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"15828df4cb3b9ae5bde291817cc9cede4e4888ae","tid":614746,"uid":179367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T06:07:34.000Z","msg":"巴打還安好？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T19:50:39.000Z","msg":"Hey巴打我係度，因為最近搞緊畢業展覽所以冇咩點update、同埋個post真係冇咩人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a97746b59302a6d04253b6aee08b637d6a5a66","tid":614746,"uid":14810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a22cb9c99055f5bf292b3de4e77a65364751660","tid":614746,"uid":81372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d841a49275d33c952acbb95b73361d2fec6cbe1","tid":614746,"uid":14810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pi